4.2 Scenario 
Feature: EXPERIENCE ITINERARY TABLE 
Then: Users want to establish experience ITINERARY 
Then: If activity moves through out different Location.
Then: User clicks to Add ITINERARY TABLE 
Then: ACTIVITY ITINERARY TABLE opens 
And: ITINERARY IS TITLED by system as the EXPERIENCE NAME from above.
Then. Organizer is adding 1 STAGE named by its LOCATION.
Then: System should be linked to MAP DATA BASE (or GOOGLE MAP platform)
Then: User can clicks directly on the map to add LOCATION NAME to the 1 STAGE
And: Sytem autocomplete the name of location at the gap when Organizer typing in.
Then: Systen finds a match at MAP And LOCATION Database
Then: Then 1 STAGE ADDED at itinerary table 
And: now displays with EXACT location name and coordenates
Then: An UBICATION SIGNAL get ATTACHED TO MAP at LOCATION SELECTED
Then: Organizer will now clicks in the 1 STAGE to add brief stage description
Then: Organizer will get balnk tex box 
Then: Organizer fill it with LOCATION BRIEF DESCRIPTION.100 characters
Then: STAGE will only show the name of LOCATION SELECTED at the ITINERERY TABLE
aND: Only by placing mouse track on the LOCATION at map USER GET stage description info.
Then: ORGANIZER clikS on the stage days number
then : Organizer can add number of days spent at that stage
Then: FOR EACH DAY seleccted sytem will show 3 categories
And: organizer will marck 3 categories by clicking progress bar at each histogram 
Then: Organizer will assigned a % VALUE 
Then FOR EACH DAY OFR EXPERINCE PLANNED.  
Then: Oranizer discribe DAYS ACTIVITY by giving each day a % at 3 different categories
Then: User add % of that day that will be dedicated to Sport, Nature, Landscapes & Sightseeing. 
And: User add % of that day that will be dedicated to Relax, free time or Mind Activities. 
And: User add % of that day that will be dedicated to People, Culture & Gastronomy. 
Then: TOTAL DAY % VALUE DAY ATTACHED TO THEM will show sumatory % values place by Organizer
And: at any given time as soon as any % value is added by orginazer to the categories 
Then; Sytem will add inmediatly value to total day % value gap below.
And: system wont allow more than 100% at total sumatory or categories gap
Then: System will always place actumatically % value for last category 
And: Until compleate 100& of day value.
And: IN case organizer not agree with last valued added
Then: Organizer can cliks on top of any category to change its value.
And: Adding a new % value to it, autoomatically wil delivery differnt value to other categries.
Then: Adding or deducing from each of categories in case going beyons total 100% day
Given: Each category is rated an total sumatory is 100%
( example:1DAY= Adventure 60% + Relax 20% + Culture 20%= total 100%
(Then if %value introduce in that order sytem would add 20% for cultre)
Then: System will now show an PIE CHART FOR EACH DAY AT ITINERARY TABLE STAGES
And: PIE CHART will be added to the STAGE INFO for EACH DAY (1 DAY= 1PIE)
And : DISPLAYED at ITINERARY TABLE FOR ACTIVITY EXPERIENCE OFFER
Then: Recorded at DATABASE EXPERINCES OFFER

